	<description><![CDATA[ 
	<p>Image Manager Extended 1.5.0 Stable</p>
	<p>Changelog (from 1.5.0 RC 1)</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Fixed: Empty margin values produced an error in IE.</li>
		<li>Fixed: Proportional dimensions calculation error.</li>
		<li>Fixed: 500 Server error if GD not installed.</li>
		<li>Added: Support for filetype groups and ability to set file types in parameters</li>
		<li>Added: Interface improvements.</li>
		<li>Added: Tooltip help dialogs.</li>
	</ul>
	<p>Changelog (from 1.5.0 beta 1)</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Fixed: Parameter issue with upload method.</li>
		<li>Fixed: Forced Upload options.</li>
		<li>Fixed: Tooltip checkbox label.</li>
		<li>Fixed: JCE Utilities Popup creation</li>
		<li>Added: Window popup!</li>
		<li>Added: Popup script requirement messages.</li>
	<ul>
	]]></description>
